I have just tried with both Bazel @0.3.1 and the present master. Both lead to the same errors reported by @KjerG, trying to build Tensorflow on the present master, too.

Interestingly, building 95ddc4e (just before the possibly breaking 7bcdcbb) seems to work (I just need to build //tensorflow/cc:cc_ops, though).

body:
I have just tried with both Bazel @0.3.1 and the present master. Both lead to the same errors reported by @KjerG, trying to build Tensorflow on the present master, too.

Interestingly, building 95ddc4e (just before the possibly breaking 7bcdcbbf) seems to work (I just need to build `//tensorflow/cc:cc_ops`, though).
